      <title>日本执政党自民党将如何选出接替岸田的新领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/how-japan-s-ruling-ldp-will-elect-new-leader-to-succeed-kishida</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党自民党定于 9 月 27 日举行党魁选举，由于该党在议会中占据主导地位，获胜者几乎肯定会接替即将离任的首相岸田文雄出任首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/how-japan-s-ruling-ldp-will-elect-new-leader-to-succeed-kishida</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 01:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与菲律宾就阿富汗人过境签证问题达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/us-philippines-agree-on-transit-of-afghans-applying-for-visas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾表示，它同意与美国允许有限数量的阿富汗国民过境前往这个东南亚国家，办理特殊移民签证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/us-philippines-agree-on-transit-of-afghans-applying-for-visas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 00:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克的亲特朗普超级政治行动委员会在亲共和党的北卡罗来纳州聘请助手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/elon-musk-s-pro-trump-super-pac-hires-canvassers-in-north-carolina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的亲特朗普超级政治行动委员会正在北卡罗来纳州招聘拉票人，这表明这位前总统的盟友担心他在最亲共和党的战场州之一的支持率会下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/elon-musk-s-pro-trump-super-pac-hires-canvassers-in-north-carolina</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 23:55:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党全国代表大会开幕，拜登将火炬传递给哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/democrats-start-convention-with-biden-passing-torch-to-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党人周一在芝加哥举行大会，赞扬乔·拜登的总统任期——并向选民发出这位决定放弃总统任期的人的最后一次呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/democrats-start-convention-with-biden-passing-torch-to-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 23:26:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
