      <title>特朗普为美联储批评辩护，考虑向购房者提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/trump-defends-fed-criticism-weighs-providing-aid-to-home-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普淡化了对他削弱美联储自主权的批评，称他应该能够自由地分享他对利率政策的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/trump-defends-fed-criticism-weighs-providing-aid-to-home-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 21:46:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乔治·桑托斯认罪，承认滥用竞选资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/george-santos-pleads-guilty-admits-misusing-campaign-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前众议员乔治桑托斯在竞选国会议员期间谎称自己曾在高盛集团和花旗集团工作，最终他承认在竞选国会议员期间犯有电信欺诈和身份盗窃罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/george-santos-pleads-guilty-admits-misusing-campaign-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 19:54:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪将在俄罗斯入侵后首次访问乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/modi-will-visit-ukraine-for-first-time-since-russia-s-invasion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪定于周五访问基辅，试图平衡与华盛顿和莫斯科的关系，但已排除在调解俄罗斯结束乌克兰战争的角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/modi-will-visit-ukraine-for-first-time-since-russia-s-invasion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
